<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qd mạt bạlṣlyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qd mạt bạlṣlyb
 ʿny hdẖạ ạlḥbyb
 fḥbh ldẖạ ʿjyb
 tʿạlwạ yạ kẖṭạẗ
 lwạhb ạlḥyạẗ
 fḥbh yʿṭy ạlnjạẗ

[C1]
   ạlqrạr- ạ̉ny ạ̉ḥbh ạ̹dẖ mạt mn ạ̉jly
   wḥbh yḥlw ạ̹dẖ gẖfr dẖnby
   tʿạlwạ dẖwqwạ wạnẓrwạ hdẖạ rby
   wmạlk qlby

[V2]
 knt fy ḥyrẗ
 bgẖyr mrsẖd
 ạ̹blys qd ạ̉dẖlny
 ḥty̱ ạ̉ty̱ ạlḥbyb
 lqlby ạlkỷyb ly
 fạtḥạaⁿ bạb ạlrjạ

[V3]
 qd ṣrt ḥty̱ ạlận
 ạ̉ʿysẖ fy ạṭmỷnạn
 ạ̹dẖ ạsmy̱ fy sfr ạlḥyạẗ
 wmskny hnạk
 mʿ zmrẗ ạlạ̉mlạk</lyrics>
<hymn_number>5929</hymn_number>
</song>